'''Pride Month 2026''' is a community event to celebrate [[Wikipedia:Pride Month|Pride Month]] for 2026. The event featured a pride-themed hub world, a charity fundraising campaign for Trans Lifeline, and several rewards for users participating. It took place from June 1, 2026 - June 30, 2026.

==Details==
On May 29, 2026, VRChat shared a post<ref>"We're hosting a party for Pride and we hope you can make it! 💃", https://x.com/VRChat/status/2060400473320858026.</ref> on their social media outlining their plans for the Pride Month 2026 event. Attached to the post was picture outlining dates for Pride Performances and more to be revealed on June 1st.

On June 1, 2026, the Pride Month 2026 event went live.<ref name="PrideAnnouncement">"HAPPY PRIDE! 🏳️‍🌈", https://x.com/VRChat/status/2061539645486477690.</ref>

==Hub world==
''See also [[VRChat Official Pride Hub]] for more detailed information.''

The VRChat Official Pride Hub is where users can come together and celebrate LGBTQIA+ community during the event. The hub features, posters, pride floats and representable flags, set in a vibrant nighttime island.

==Pride Campaign==
[[File:PrideMonth2026 We Did It!.png|thumb|Finished Pride Campaign 2025 menu screenshot]]
The Pride Campaign is a charity fundraising campaign for Trans Lifeline, a trans-led nonprofit that offers direct emotional and financial support to trans people in crisis.<ref name="PrideAnnouncement" /> VRChat will be donating $100,000USD to Trans Lifeline.

Users can participate and track progress by navigating to the Pride Event tab in the VRC+ page. By participating in the campaign, users can earn several rewards.

===Rewards===
Users that participate during the pride campaign are subject to the following rewards:

* Pride Starter Bundle
** Available to everyone
** "VRCat Celebrates Pride" [[Stickers|sticker]]

* Loud & Proud
** Available to users who gifted once
** "Stardust" [[Warp Effects|warp effect]]

* Double the Love
** Available to users who gifted twice
** "Neon Star" [[Portals|portal]]

* Rainbow Legend
** Available to users who gifted 5 times
** "Christopher Cloud" [[Items|item]]

* Community Spirit Reward
** Available to everyone once the community goal is reached
** "Pride Pin" [[Accessories|accessory]]

* Pride 2026 Badge
** Available to users that claim the "Pride Starter Bundle", "Loud & Proud", "Double the Love", and "Rainbow Legend" rewards.
** "Pride Supporter 2026" [[Badges|badge]]

