===Hype Train===
<!-- add images for hype train -->
During the event, a limited time Hype Train feature was added. When any user uses gift drops twice within 5 minutes, a Hype Train will start.

Hype Trains can be started in any world and in any instance. To complete a Hype Train, users need to gift drop a total of 50 times, before the timer runs down. After a gift drop is sent, users have 5 minutes to send another gift drop before the Hype Train ends, and each gift drop will reset the timer.

Users that are in the instance of a successful Hype Train will receive the "Extravagant Pride Fan" item.

